o: Lee James Brown (born 10 August 1990) is an English professional footballer who plays as a left-back for League One club Portsmouth. Brown formerly played for Queens Park Rangers, Salisbury City, Hayes & Yeading United and Bristol Rovers, spending seven seasons with the latter club and amassing 321 appearances. He has played for the England C national team.
